{"tid":158704,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州火鍋店回收湯底 重複利用560次","createTime":"2017-03-16T12:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T06:09:47.000Z","uid":828,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"136627e6469ef58bd05da06ad91fc28c140deaf6","tid":158704,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170316/1077741/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170316%2F1077741%2F&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e7ec6d20\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170316/1077741/</a><br />\n<br />\n香噴噴的麻辣火鍋是不少人冬天解饞的最愛，但廣東公共頻道DV現場調查組日前臥底暗訪，赫然發現驚人內幕，一家位於廣州的知名火鍋店，竟把食客吃剩的紅油湯底，由服務員帶到後廚裝進餿水桶，等食客離去後，廚房員工深夜就開始打撈餿水桶裡的油，裝入旁邊一個不銹鋼桶內。第二天中午11時，這名廚師就開始熬製火鍋鍋底，把回收紅油進行再加工。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dc175ae273f66cc0dadd9cc9d23dd3b96348f5","tid":158704,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:25:27.000Z","msg":"符合國情"},{"pid":"a8a9412b7a9cfe896cac931c48dc3e3448bc67c5","tid":158704,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"啱曬成日&quot;返&quot;大陸享受嘅一部分傻閪香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做大爺丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46a41ab824a3b5d5362f5dd052c6b3470c02d3f","tid":158704,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"好多支那人 甚至香港人<br />\n<br />\n都話強國野好食過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abc115dfda1eb4497daf157ffba0237aa1ae9a2","tid":158704,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-la